title: Photo Life Buyers Guide - 2014  CA
description:
Photo Life Buyer's Guide - 2014  CA

124 Pages | HQ PDF | English | 15 MB 


Filled with reviews, specs and prices of more than 280 new products, the Photo Life experts will help you make smart choices of photo gear to match your needs and preferences. The Buyers' Guide 2014 features the latest in digital cameras, lenses, tripods, action cams, lighting equipment, apps, software, printers and more.
